name: Musicals'Songs
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: musical songs
des: A five, six, seven, eight! Come on everyone. Why don't we test our knowledge... and all that jazz! In this Alexa skill, the user will be quizzed on what songs come from which musical. There are ten questions per quiz and your quiz will be randomized, so you will get a different one every time! Rack up points with every answer you get right, and at the end of the quiz see how you did! Now, go enjoy reminiscing about popular musicals' songs and break a leg. Lights...camera.........ACTION!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
